li.al:
Officials assigned to work for the Planning Element and those
                who have official duties with the Planning Element as well as
                their spouses and dependent members of their families;

Exemption for themselves and for their spouses and dependent
                members of the family from visa fees and immigration
                restrictions or aliens registration procedures;

Exemption from Danish taxation on the salaries and all other
                remuneration paid to them by the Planning Element and by their
                home states. Denmark retains the right to tax income from other sources;

In regard to foreign exchange, including holding accounts in
                foreign currencies, enjoyment of the same facilities as are
                accorded to diplomats accredited to the Government;

The privileges and immunities mentioned in this article are
                granted in the interest of the Planning Element and the
                SHIRBRIG, and not for the personal benefit of the officials themselves;

Immuniteit van rechtsvervolging met betrekking tot het door
                hen gesproken of geschreven woord en alle door hen in de
                uitoefening van hun officiële functie verrichte handelingen;

Ontheffing voor henzelf en voor hun echtgenoten en de van hen
                afhankelijke gezinsleden van visumheffingen en inreisbeperkingen
                of vreemdelingenregistratie;
